{"tid":1512380,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"#社畜嘅抗爭! 簡單一步改變輿論!","createTime":"2019-08-28T00:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T01:58:37.000Z","uid":34423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b7444eeacb2f4b9ba7742115850b593f45a1bf54","tid":1512380,"uid":34423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:56:48.000Z","msg":"大家都知道基本上所有免費報都係奶共<br />\n<br />\n尤其係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">am730</span></span>嗰啲廢紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但偏偏就係好多打工仔同埋師奶呀叔嘅朝早讀物<br />\n<br />\nStep 1<br />\n我地未必個個人都上到前線<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但免費報紙個個都可以攞!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以一人出多少少力<br />\n早少少出門口 行前兩步<br />\n攞晒啲報紙<br />\n全部掉晒去回收箱!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nStep 2<br />\n返Office工嘅各位<br />\n不防可以買下蘋果<br />\n放喺公司Pantry<br />\n等同事有個吸收下資訊嘅機會<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁小事 你唔係有藉口唔做呀嘛?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港!<br />\n時代革命!"},{"pid":"6ba45c11179e97c0893b84f4c6629fefddf53b54","tid":1512380,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CEqOUyf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCEqOUyf.jpg&h=2722f546&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NSAWdB2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNSAWdB2.jpg&h=7e1fa5a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dced3c5a25ac98c429cdd0330666053ddd51835f","tid":1512380,"uid":34423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:57:24.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"74b938b9b1262422a03e3f9c5e29622a56b9288b","tid":1512380,"uid":34423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:57:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid"